THX for the upload 1st of all. I ve tried to do it for myu nokia 5800. It does not read the map. The old map works fine. Any ideea how to fix it for mobile devices?

-get a sd card: 4gb
-format it to fat32
-create a folder in it named: garmin
-copy the .img to the folder
-call the .img file gmapsupp.img
-put the sd card in the slot of your nav system
-start it and the map will load automaticly (if not go to settings, maps, map info and check the map of 2011)
-nav on :D
